aweme_list.desc: The most beautiful restaurant in New Jersey. Rat’s Restaurant, nestled in the charming grounds of the @groundsforsculpture in New Jersey, offers a dining experience like no other. With its charming ambiance inspired by Claude Monet’s gardens in Giverny, France, this enchanting eatery transports guests to the heart of a European countryside villa. From exquisite French-inspired cuisine to its magical surroundings, every visit to Rat’s is a journey into a world of culinary delight and cultural immersion. Rat’s Restaurant overlooks sculptures in the park as well as a lily-pond and a bridge.  @rats.restaurant  📍	16 Fairgrounds Rd, Hamilton, NJ 08619 #ratsrestaurant #groundsforsculpture #hamiltonnj #njrestaurants #njfoodie
